    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>quick cook spaghetti</strong> and <strong>halved Tenderstem</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook for 2-3 min or until everything is cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the<strong> spaghetti & Tenderstem</strong>, reserving a cup of the <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p>",
