      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mushrooms are browned, reduce the heat to medium-high</p><p>Add your <strong>roasted garlic paste </strong>to the pan with the <strong>tomato paste </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cook for a further 2-3 min or until fragrant</p>",
