    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>sun-dried tomato pesto, soft cheese</strong> and <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> to the pan with a splash of the <strong>reserved</strong> <strong>starchy pasta water </strong>and stir it all together</p>",
