    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained spaghetti & Tenderstem</strong> to the pan and give everything a good mix up until fully coated in the sauce</p><p>Remove the pan from the heat and stir through <strong>half </strong>your <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) – this is your <strong>creamy sun-dried tomato, mushroom & broccoli spaghetti</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
